snippet.title: The Thaumaturge | Console Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
No one understands inner demons and deep-rooted human flaws better than Wiktor Szulski, a seasoned thaumaturge who perceives the subtle imprints of human emotion while hunting folklore-inspired monsters on the streets of 1905 Warsaw. #TheThaumaturge will arrive on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S on December 4th. 

🎮Play the demo now!
PlayStation 5: https://store.playstation.com/en-pl/product/EP4361-PPSA25759_00-0THAUMATURGEDEMO
Xbox Series X|S: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/the-thaumaturge-demo/9nflt5rphjwr
